snippet.title: TERE DIL MEIN - Rito Riba | Elvish Yadav & Jannat Zubair | Rajat Nagpal | Rana Sotal | Anshul Garg
snippet.description:
Anshul Garg presents Tere Dil Mein featuring Elvish Yadav & Jannat Zubair.

Audio Credits :-
Singer : Rito Riba
Music Composer : Rajat nagpal
Lyrics : Rana sotal
Music composed , produced and programmed by : Rajat Nagpal 
Mixed and Mastered by : Shadab Rayeen 
Guitars : Rhythm Shaw 
Dholak & Tabla Raju : Sardar and Team 
Chorus : Sonu 
Harmonium : Paras Chopra 
Keys : Rajat Nagpal
Recorded by Rahul Sharma @ Studio 504

Video Credits :-
Production house-Rs films and 
Production
Director : Anishh 2.O
EP : Rahul Sahel 
Director Ad : Rajat Yadav & Aashish
Dop : Vikcee
Dop Ac : Rahul Sabharwal
Ac : Rashwinder
Choregrapher : Sumit
Production managar : Rohit gaur,saksham mehta,gulshan,Gurpreet

Elvish and jannat makeup : Prabh makeover
Art : Karma art
Edit & D : -Inkblaze Studio
VFX : Visuals by potter
Stylist : Rajat Manchanda 
Bts : Harsh
Elvish Hair Stylist : Harry
Elvish Makeup : Parbh Makeoverz
Jannat Hair & Makeup : Ruhi Makeoverz
Junior casting : Aamir Qureshi 
Junior makeup : Sunny 

PlayDMF Team :-

Vice President : Raghav Sharma ( Pratick Sharma)
Label Manager : Sankalp Garg
Project Head : Gaurav Arora
Legal & Digital Manager : Ashima Chauhan
PlayDMF Team : Aansi Agrawal & Anshu Prasad

Special Thanks : Virgin Music India

Special Thanks : Virgin Music India
https://www.virginmusic.com/

Virgin Music India Team :-
Head : Amit Sharma 
Team : Nagesh Jadhav, Kajal Israni, Amol Suryavanshi, Lavanya Das, Nishtha Sikroria

Lyrics :-
Rabb maan liya tujhko 
Jagg maan liya tujhko 
Tu he hai dunia meri 
Sabb maan liya tujhko,,

Maanga  jo paaya vahi  ,,

Dekh tere dil may 
Dil may dil may 
Dil may dil may yaara  toh nhi
Mai khogea khogea khogea khogea yaara hu kahi ,,

Bachkay ray bachkay deewane,,
Tu naino kay khel na jaane ,,


Tu meri jaan hai yaara ,,
Tu he hai jaan say pyara ,,
Sunali ve Sunlai ve dildara
Dhadkan banke rehna yaara ,,
Apna mujhey kehna yaara ,
Sunali ve Sunlai ve dildara ,

Tujhey yaar kahay
Jisay pyaar kahay 
Humey toh hogea hai vahi , 

Dekh tere dil may 
Dil may dil may 
Dil may dil may yaara  toh nhi
Mai khogea khogea ,,
khogea khogea khogea yaara hu kahi ,,

#teredilmein #elvishyadav #elvish #jannat #jannatzubair #ritoriba

Song: Gal Sun (Je Tu Labda Wafa Firda)
Singer: Sabaat Batin
Lyrics/Composition: Sabaat Batin
Rapper: Rackstar
Music Prod. Rackstar
Mix/Master: Rackstar
Director: Rafaqat Ali
Label: SkillMill Records

lyrics:
Je Tu Labda Wafa Firda Nahi Labni
Roop Dooja Ae Saza Da Sajan Sajni
Jadon Apna Begana Hoya Takdeya Nahi
Rondeyaan Nu Thaan Nahi Tenu Ae Labni
Asi Aa Deewane Bas
Te Sade Kol Khazane Nai
Te Jinna Kol Khazane Nai
Laundi Ohna Naal Yaraane Nai
Duniya Matlabi Duniya
Sun Ke Na Kar Ansuniyaan
Sun O Gal Sun Dilbar Jaani
Jag Wafa Teri Nadaani
Na Koi Tere Gham Da Haani
Rajak ve Jhuthe Jhuthi Rani
Jhuthi Rani Jhuthi Rani Jhuthi Rani
Raja Jhuthe Jhuthi Rani
Oh Jhuthi Rani Jhuthi Rani
Main Fadhan Ohde Dhokhe Aggon Pandi Aa Kahani
Oh Kehndi Kar Vishvaas Haigi Nahiyo Wish Khaas
Dena Chaundi Dhokha Nahi Si Ho Gayi Naadaani
Naadaan Nahi Ae Hoshiyar Bahot
Duniya Ae Kise Di Nahi Ede Yaar Bahut
Tu Maan Baitha Ehnu Aakhri
Janda Nahi Veere Haige Ehde Yaar Bahut
Na Kari Yaara Pyar Nahin Milni Wafa
Ohna Pyar Haiga Sarna Ni Apni Dafa
Haan Kari Izhaar Na Tu Kari Aitbaar
Tu Kinu Sooli Chadhna Main Likh ke Dawan
Chann Chann Aakhein Jihnu Raataan Ohne Pauniyan Ne
Pani Jihne Rang Chadhaya Aggaan Ohne Launiyan Ne
Kal Kujh Nai Je Sochna Te Soch Ajj Hi
Ajj Baras Pai Kal Hona Gajj Hi
Kar Faisla Je Ajj Kal Fer Hona Kakh Ni
Baki Daseya Main Agge Yaara Teri Marzi
Sun O Gal Sun Dilbar Jaani
Jag Wafa Teri Naadaani
Na Koi Tere Gham Da Haani
Raja Jhoothe Jhoothi Rani
Koi Nahi Daur Reh Gaye Ve
Pyara Te Khumaraan De
O Bikde Ne Dil Jaani Lakha Te Hazara Che Vey
Koi Nai Daur Reh Gaye Ve
Pyara Te Khumaraan De

snippet.description:
Nas Nas Kyu Dukhe ‡§™‡§ø‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§Æ‡•á‡§∞‡•Ä ‡§®‡§∏ ‡§®‡§∏ ‡§ï‡•á ‡§π‡•ã ‡§¶‡•Å‡§ñ‡•á || Anjali Raghav & Karan Chaudhary || Brajbhasha Song 


Piya Meri Nas Nas Kyun Dookhei
Balam Meri Nas Nas Kyun Dookhei
 
Na Hilo Jaye.. Na Chigo
Aaj Meri Chhati Si Toote
Piya Meri Nas Nas Kyun Dookhei...

Gori Toye Nazar Lagi Deekhei
Haan Gori Nazar Lagi Deekhei
Ja Sabre Gaam Me Top Lugai Bas Tu Hi Deekhe

Gori Toye Nazar Lagi Deekhei...

Haan Ghar Te Nikru Saj Dhaj Ke
Moye Toke Log Lugai
Koi Radua Maare Siti
Dekh Koi Bolo Butterfly

Toye Laad Kare Je Ghar Kunve Ki
Sagri Chachi Tayi
Aur Naam Bata De Raduan Ko
Do Minute Me Karu Kutayi

Haan Tu Bhi Kare Na Laad Piya
Mope Daanti Si Meense

Gori Toye Nazar Lagi Deekhei...

Arey Bano Chaudhary Ghoome
Sab Din Mope Kaam Karave
Ho.. Phoonk Jaray Du Ghar Ghoore Ku
Aisi Mann Mein Aave

Arey Raakh Sabar Meri Dhanno
Kayko Tu Itni Ghabrave
Aur Lal Kilo Tere Naam Karay Du
Ek Ber Muskaye De

Moye Dekh Ke Devar Ek Aankh Te
Photo So Kheenche

Gori Toye Nazar Lagi Deekhei...
*
Piya Mero Jee So Cho Ghabrave
Rang Mero Neelo Padto Aawe
Baidh Bulaye De...
Jhaaro Jaldi Tu Moku Lagvaye De...

Mat Na Leve Tension Pyari
Tote Karu Laad Main Bhari..
Chhappar Phaar Kein...
Teri Nazar Utaaru Mantar Maar Kein..

snippet.title: Hawaon Ne Yeh Kaha (Lyrical Video) | Udit Narayan | Hrithik Roshan | Ameesha Patel
snippet.description:
Hawaon Ne Yeh Kaha is a soft and romantic melody sung by Udit Narayan, featuring the beautiful pairing of Hrithik Roshan and Ameesha Patel from the movie Aap Mujhe Achche Lagne Lage. 
This song captures young love, innocence, and heartfelt emotions beautifully, making it a timeless favourite for Bollywood romance lovers. 

Credits: 
Singer: Udit Narayan
Music: Rajesh Roshan
Lyrics: Dev Kohli
Movie: Aap Mujhe Achche Lagne Lage
Starring: Hrithik Roshan, Ameesha Patel
Director: Vikram Bhatt
Producer: Rohit Kumar
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics: 

[Nahin marna ganwara pyaar mein 

Tumse yeh kehna hai 

Tumhein bhi zinda rehna hai 

Mujhe bhi zinda rehna hai] 

Kabhi aasaan, kabhi mushkil 

Ajab hain pyaar ki raahein 

Kabhi aasaan, kabhi mushkil 

Ajab hain pyaar ki raahein 

Magar jo pyaar karte hain 

Kabhi bharte nahin aahein 


Hawaon ne yeh kaha 

Fizaon ne yeh kaha 

Aayi pyaar ki ye rut badi tufani 

Tu darna na o meri rani 

Badlega yeh mausam ari deewani 

Hum likhenge prem kahani

Ajab hain pyaar ki raahein 

Kabhi aasaan, kabhi mushkil

Gardish mein hi sahi 

Yeh sitare humnashin 

Gardish mein hi sahi 

Yeh sitare humnashin 

Dhoondhegi kal hamein 

Phir bahaarein humnashin 

Imtehan pyaar ke roz hote nahin 

Pyaar wale kabhi sabra khote nahi 

Mohabbat ho hi jaati hai 

Mohabbat ki nahi jaati 

Yeh aisi cheez hai jo sabke 

Hisse mein nahi aati

Powerful Shiva Bhakti Songs is a sacred collection of Kannada devotional hymns dedicated to Lord Shiva, the supreme symbol of devotion, renunciation, and divine consciousness. Sacred stotrams like Lingashtakam are traditionally listened to on Monday, an auspicious day for Shiva worship.

These Monday Shiva Bhakti Geethegalu are ideal for daily prayer, Monday pooja, early morning chanting, meditation, and Shiva aradhana, creating a calm and spiritually uplifting atmosphere.

When: Sunday, January 18, 2026 at 1:30 PM local time

Where: Holkar Stadium, Indore

What to expect: The venue has traditionally been a batter's paradise and it is unlikely to be any different on Sunday. The small boundaries should aid India's free-stroking batters, but New Zealand - who have surprised the hosts by punching above their weight in the series - cannot be underestimated, particularly a certain Daryl Mitchell. But all eyes will be on Rohit and Kohli.

Team News

India

India may bring in Arshdeep for the decider even as but there is unlikely to be any change in the batting line-up. Nitish Reddy, who has not lived up to expectations since the century at MCG in BGT more than a year ago, will be under scrutiny. It will be a big match for him.

Probable XI: Shubman Gill (c), Rohit Sharma, Virat Kohli, Shreyas Iyer, KL Rahul (wk) Ravindra Jadeja, Nitish Kumar Reddy, Harshit Rana, Kuldeep Yadav, Mohammed Siraj, Arshdeep Singh.

New Zealand

New Zealand are on the brink of a historic series win and, if they do pull it off, it will be an incredible achievement for a side missing several of their ODI regulars - Kane Williamson, Rachin Ravindra, Matt Henry and Mitchell Santner among others. Kyle Jamieson has tested Indian batters, Mitchell has given the Indian bowlers sleepless nights, and then there is the 31-year-old left-arm spinner Lennox, who has managed to contain otherwise unstoppable Indian batters in his debut game in Rajkot.

Probable XI: Devon Conway, Henry Nicholls, Will Young, Daryl Mitchell, Glenn Phillips, Mitchell Hay (wk), Michael Bracewell (c), Zakary Foulkes, Kristian Clarke, Kyle Jamieson, Jayden Lennox.

About The Game
Quarantine Zone is a dark and intense post-apocalyptic strategy game where your role is to command the last surviving blockade in a world infected by a deadly virus. In this Malayalam gameplay, we dive deep into the harsh reality of inspecting survivors for signs of the zombie virus‚Äîdeciding whether to trust, quarantine, or liquidate them. Each choice you make could save lives or doom humanity. Expand your base, upgrade defenses, and prepare for relentless infected hordes. Every decision has weight, and every mistake has a cost. If you love survival decision-making games like Frostpunk or This War of Mine, Quarantine Zone will test your morals and strategy skills to the edge. Watch as we explore this brutal, choice-driven experience in full Malayalam commentary. 
Game: Quarantine zone
Language: Malayalam

Each choice you make could save lives or doom humanity. Expand your base, upgrade defenses, and prepare for relentless infected hordes. Every decision has weight, and every mistake has a cost. If you love survival decision-making games like Frostpunk or This War of Mine, Quarantine Zone will test your morals and strategy skills to the edge. Watch as we explore this brutal, choice-driven experience in full Malayalam commentary. 
Game: Quarantine zone
Language: Malayalam
